channel.title: WebClient Error Thing
channel.description:
This is really [b]pissing[/b] me the [b]HELL[/b] off! [b]I tried so many times.. I even googled, I didn't find anything! [/b] [IMG]http://i884.photobucket.com/albums/ac47/tonyboloney2/helppl.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt]This shows up [b]EVERY[/b] time I upload a [b]new[/b] client.jar or my cache.. I have to upload it to [b]FileDen[/b] because it is the [b]ONLY[/b][b]file hosting website[/b] that works for me. :'( Please tell me what the problem is..[/size]
